The world is built  of communities of shared interests. (People seeking freedom for Ukraine, football fans following their favourite clubs, ...)

But languages come in the way.

Help us in joining the communities across language borders.

Twitter Crowd Translation (TCT) is an infrastructure for fast translation of twitter content with the help of you, members of these communities.


Producer 
	- author producing tweets in source language
	- gains bigger audience and visibility
Translator/Evaluator
	- bilingual person providing translation from source to target language / score of translations
	- language practice
Consumer 
	- person requesting translation to target language
	- gains direct access to forein content


Tweets compete for translation
